 《Holo Live》衍生动作游戏《Holo X Break》制作中，5代学生将担任可玩角色https://www.moguravr.com/holo-x-break-game-hololive/井文 Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:32:34 +0000 VTuberホロライブHolo X Break https://www.moguravr.com/?p=247429 <p>以女性VTuber组合“Hololive”为主题的新动作游戏“Holo X Break”现已发布。该游戏目前正在制作中，并在 Steam 销售网站上宣传为“即将推出”。 “Holo X Br [...]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/holo-x-break-game-hololive/">《Holo Live》衍生动作游戏《Holo X Break》正在制作中，第 5 代学生</a>首次在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上作为可玩角色出现。</p> ; <p>以女性VTuber组合“Hololive”为主题的新动作游戏《 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2719150/Holo_X_Break/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holo X Break</a> 》现已公布。该游戏目前正在制作中，并在<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2719150/Holo_X_Break/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam 销售网站</a>上宣传为“即将推出”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.syh72bfrzm5w-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.syh72bfrzm5w-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.syh72bfrzm5w-jpg.webp 616w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.syh72bfrzm5w-300x172.webp 300w" width="616" height="353" /></a></p><p> 《Holo X Break》是由衍生游戏《 <a href="https://kay-yu.itch.io/holocure" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HoloCure</a> 》的开发者<a href="https://twitter.com/kaynimatic" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kay Yu</a>创作的游戏。该类型是一款皮带卷轴动作游戏。可以使用“Hololive”第五代成员四四郎牡丹和奥玛鲁波尔卡等作为可玩角色。<br />此外，《Holive》衍生游戏的游戏品牌“holo Indie”正在发行。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.tad44tmissys-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.tad44tmissys-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.tad44tmissys-jpg.webp 600w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.tad44tmissys-300x169.webp 300w" width="600" height="337" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.m4t3svik16ue-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.m4t3svik16ue-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.m4t3svik16ue-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.m4t3svik16ue-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.m4t3svik16ue-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.m4t3svik16ue-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.m4t3svik16ue-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.xmxqwwkj0pva-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.xmxqwwkj0pva-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.xmxqwwkj0pva-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.xmxqwwkj0pva-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6becdf03c41cc4f14d41c49f1827d240-kix.xmxqwwkj0pva-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/6