03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.1s9shyhtcujn-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>对于两个长期在VRChat工作的人来说，这个VR空间，以及三丽鸥VFES的第三次出现，已经不再是一个平台。在做MC的同时，我们会一边做MC，一边继续演绎经典歌曲。在《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvQPlP0-enE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>七层列车</strong></a>》中，观众们也通过让观众动起来的编舞营造出一种团结感，下一首代表歌曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9uvVhwEj1Zw" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Insure Existence</strong></a> 》也让人兴奋不已。</p><p>当我被比去年更加精致的舞蹈表演所吸引时，我也不忘记向观众们喊话。上半场、下半场，说出歌中的歌词。最后，动情演唱的《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B6c9wtENFgI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>PROOF</strong></a> 》和《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D91jwPSEqpQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Find Yours</strong></a> 》，引起了他们的胸腔共鸣，度过了非常满意的live。</p><h2>富士葵</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.up5etkxc7etm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>这是Sanrio VFES<a href="https://twitter.com/fuji_aoi_0618" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>富士葵</strong></a>第二次登场。在出现在舞台后部的同时，他们连唱《<strong>相关记忆</strong>》和《<strong>意大利餐厅</strong>》，用拉长的歌声将场地一下子渲染得色彩斑斓。</p><p>在上届三丽鸥VFES中，苍井富士先生以有力的“U”演唱翻唱了VAUNDY的《 <strong>Monster Hananga</strong> 》。沿着花路行走时发出的锈迹斑斑的高音，不仅从两侧传来，就连二楼也传来。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.g1kll3yh4xsw-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.z9bsrwgkazva-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" load