h3rul-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><a href="https://twitter.com/773urara" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>乌拉拉·纳纳米（Urara Nanami）</strong></a>是一位平行歌手，在真实和虚拟之间旅行。这是Sanrio VFE的首次出现。</p><p>从第一首歌开始，原始歌曲“<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aJj5yJfXQ_E" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>红色气球</strong></a>”出现在舞台后面，令人印象深刻的是我已经习惯了舞台，例如在花路上唱歌和唱歌，同时向周围的观众挥手。根据她的动作，蓬松和蓬松的头发和服装很棒。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.fn9ho2r4qzn2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy"