后一场演唱了“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N-4cXU_lU8U" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Kiwame -tekawaii</strong></a> ”刚刚发布的“ Kiwame -tekawaii”，结束了大约30分钟的舞台。凭借完整的时间表现和MC，感觉就像是一个豪华的时期，它传达了那些最初认识她的人的魅力。</p><h2> Inaba Hana</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>这是第三次出现， <a href="https://twitter.com/Haneru_Inaba" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Henel Inaba</strong></a>被称为大型Sanrio情人。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2021/12/202112131213648000-300x169.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> Vtuber Inaba Haneru访问虚拟“ Sanrio Puroland”？</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2"> 12月12日（Sun）Animae Vtuber Henel Inaba Henel将在“ Sanrio Puroland”上进行YouTube Live发行。许多VRCHAT用户会见了Henel Inaba，并发出了令人惊讶的声音[＆Hel ...</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTUBER</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2021.12.13</span></div></div></div><p>过去，她在虚拟舞台上爆炸了对庞贝林的热爱，并在Virtual Puro舞台上演唱了许多Sanrio歌曲，但是这次她从Cinnamorol的“ <strong>Chu-Chu-chu</strong> ”开始。在MC中，在谈论布丁的爱情时，他唱了Beatcats的“ <strong>Zigzag Love</strong> ”，被列为“现在最沉迷的Sanrio的Sanrio集团”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/upload